<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
    }
    
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;"><a style="color:#ffffff;" href="{{{pass_recover_url}}}" class="button">Reset Password</a></div>
      <p>This link will expire in {{expiryTime}} hours. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you're having trouble clicking the "Reset Password" button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
      <p>{{{pass_recover_url}}}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>